annonstext:
Embedded Linux Test Engineer - Python

Are you an experienced Python test developer that has worked with embedded systems? 
Do you like to tinker with your Raspberry Pi, Arduino, Beaglebone in your spare time?

Meriting competencies:
- Experience ( 5 years) within SW development/test in embedded systems
- Python development 
- Test automation using Python
- Git
- Experience in CI/CD using Jenkins or equivalent
- Working experience of Embedded Linux preferably in a switch or router
- Exposure to Linux networking
- Some exposure to C development
- Fluent in English
